### 使用模板发送邮件的示例

@worker_url = https://your-worker.workers.dev

### 1. 发送欢迎邮件
POST {{worker_url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "welcome",
  "templateData": {
    "userName": "张三",
    "activationLink": "https://example.com/activate?token=abc123"
  },
  "from": "noreply@yourdomain.com",
  "to": "user@example.com"
}

### 2. 发送验证码邮件
POST {{worker_url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "verificationCode",
  "templateData": {
    "code": "123456",
    "expiryMinutes": 10
  },
  "from": "noreply@yourdomain.com",
  "to": "user@example.com"
}

### 3. 发送密码重置邮件
POST {{worker_url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "passwordReset",
  "templateData": {
    "userName": "李四",
    "resetLink": "https://example.com/reset-password?token=xyz789",
    "expiryHours": 1
  },
  "from": "security@yourdomain.com",
  "to": "user@example.com"
}

### 4. 发送订单确认邮件
POST {{worker_url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "orderConfirmation",
  "templateData": {
    "orderNumber": "ORD-2025-001234",
    "orderDate": "2025-11-03 16:30:00",
    "orderTotal": 299.00,
    "items": [
      {
        "name": "商品A",
        "quantity": 1,
        "price": 199.00
      },
      {
        "name": "商品B",
        "quantity": 2,
        "price": 50.00
      }
    ],
    "orderUrl": "https://example.com/orders/ORD-2025-001234"
  },
  "from": "orders@yourdomain.com",
  "to": "customer@example.com"
}

### 5. 发送信息通知（info 类型）
POST {{worker_url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "notification",
  "templateData": {
    "title": "账号信息更新",
    "message": "您的账号信息已成功更新。如果这不是您本人的操作，请立即联系客服。",
    "type": "info",
    "actionText": "查看账号",
    "actionUrl": "https://example.com/account"
  },
  "from": "noreply@yourdomain.com",
  "to": "user@example.com"
}

### 6. 发送成功通知
POST {{worker_url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "notification",
  "templateData": {
    "title": "支付成功",
    "message": "您的支付已成功处理。订单将在 24 小时内发货。",
    "type": "success",
    "actionText": "查看订单",
    "actionUrl": "https://example.com/orders"
  },
  "from": "noreply@yourdomain.com",
  "to": "customer@example.com"
}

### 7. 发送警告通知
POST {{worker_url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "notification",
  "templateData": {
    "title": "账号安全警告",
    "message": "我们检测到您的账号在异常地点登录。如果这是您本人的操作，请忽略此消息。",
    "type": "warning",
    "actionText": "确认登录",
    "actionUrl": "https://example.com/security/confirm"
  },
  "from": "security@yourdomain.com",
  "to": "user@example.com"
}

### 8. 发送错误通知
POST {{worker_url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "notification",
  "templateData": {
    "title": "支付失败",
    "message": "很抱歉，您的支付处理失败。请检查您的支付信息后重试。",
    "type": "error",
    "actionText": "重新支付",
    "actionUrl": "https://example.com/checkout"
  },
  "from": "noreply@yourdomain.com",
  "to": "customer@example.com"
}
